title: Bill Of Materials
description: This dashboard shows how to model a BOM in Neo4j and query the BOM as a graph.

title: Citation Graph
description: A dashboard built on top of the DBLP Citation Network, showing how to visualize the results of algorithms with an embedded Bloom iFrame.

title: Dad Jokes
description: A collection of dad jokes from twitter, analyzed and reconciled using Google's NLP API.

title: Domain Names
description: A dashboard containing information about the owners, providers and status of domains in New Caledonia, dataset kindly provided by OPT Nouvelle Caledonie (https://github.com/opt-nc).

title: Financial Intelligence
description: A demo dashboard created on the US Financial Crimes Enforcement Network.

title: Graph Assessment
description: A demo by the Neo4j Customer Success team - a tool to measure and improve graph maturity in an organization.

title: Interactive Rail Planner
description: Explore the EU rail network as a graph, and try out route planning using Dijkstra's algorithm.

title: Movies Dashboard
description: A basic dashboard built on top of the Neo4j movie database, as used in the Neo4j graph academy.

title: Recommendations Dashboard
description: An extension of the movies dashboard with more complex Cypher and customized visualizations.

title: Twitter Dashboard
description: A dashboard that contains the network of the Neo4j Twitter community.

title: WineRatings
description: An interactive dashboard showing wines from around the world, including their ratings and price information.
